{"tid":1180424,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【韓娛圈醜聞】崔鍾訓涉集體強姦指拘留不合理 法院駁回申請","createTime":"2019-05-31T22:29:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-31T22:54:07.000Z","uid":143093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0eb05d109d323bed1534170ac39b19928b8f5ed2","tid":1180424,"uid":143093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T22:29:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GGHEn5w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGGHEn5w.jpg&h=2d59236e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n韓國男團FT Island前隊長崔鍾訓，早前被爆跟男歌手鄭俊英等人涉集體強姦，有指受害女子多達7人，檢方早前以「特殊強姦罪」等嫌疑，申請對崔鍾訓及另外兩名涉案人士的拘留令，當中一人是出名女團成員的胞兄權某，法院於本月9日宣佈頒拘留令，令崔鍾訓成為繼鄭俊英之後，第二位被拘留的藝人。<br />\n而崔鍾訓方面，以「拘留不當」為由，向法院申請再次判斷拘留令是否合理，首爾中央地方法院於今日韓國時間下午2時，就有關崔鍾訓的拘留令進行審查，預計於今日下午作出決定。<br />\n如法院判崔鍾訓的拘留「不合理」，崔鍾訓將立即獲得釋放，於不拘留的狀態下接受調查。<br />\n隨後法院駁回崔鍾訓的申請，崔鍾訓將繼續被拘留受查。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190531/59661867\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190531%2F59661867&d=RSiYdbgXC1SHA4i8VFLgbahYowssEfWxGXKUUX6%2FcpY%3D&h=c86e6d16\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190531%2F59661867&h=13ce9a00\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190531/59661867</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9NNMNxF.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9NNMNxF.gif&h=9ef3becd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e54825cf73ba953aea5a3265d6893291e20b493a","tid":1180424,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T22:31:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/YfxgQ7w.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYfxgQ7w.gif&h=5e8903c2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5a68842a6a4abe182bda5283348b48